OL,3,CInside the new #5m respiratory ward
OL,4,Caimed at cutting A&E waiting times
OL,6,FA new multi-million pound respiratory
OL,7,Fward will help reduce long waiting
OL,8,Ftimes in accident and emergency,
OL,9,Faccording to NHS bosses.
OL,11,FThe #5 million unit will increase the
OL,12,Ftotal number of beds at Medway
OL,13,FMaritime Hospital by 33, when it opens
OL,14,Fto patients in the coming days.
OL,16,FManagers told ITV News Meridian that
OL,17,Ftheir A&E department was under "a
OL,18,Fgreat deal of pressure" with many
OL,19,Fpatients attending with more "complex
OL,20,Fneeds" in recent years.
