OL,3,CInside the new #5m respiratory ward
OL,4,Caimed at cutting A&E waiting times
OL,6,FMedway NHS Foundation Trust's chief
OL,7,Foperating officer, Nick Sinclair,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We've done a lot of work
OL,9,Frecently on reducing long wait times
OL,10,Fin our emergency department through
OL,11,Fimproving efficiency processes.
OL,13,F"However, we get to a point where we
OL,14,Fneed additional bed capacity to manage
OL,15,Fthat increasing demand."
OL,17,FIn March, 77.4% of patients attending
OL,18,FMedway Maritime's emergency department
OL,19,Fwaited less than four hours to be seen.
