OL,3,CInside the new #5m respiratory ward
OL,4,Caimed at cutting A&E waiting times
OL,6,FThe official figures show that 4,124
OL,7,Fpatients waited more than four hours
OL,8,Fto be seen in that month alone.
OL,10,FThe new facility, funded by NHS
OL,11,FEngland, has also been designed to
OL,12,Fprepare for potential future pandemics.
OL,14,FThe three-bed bays are all sealed from
OL,15,Fcommunal areas by automatic glass
OL,16,Fdoors to try to reduce the risk of
OL,17,Finfections spreading.
