OL,3,CInside the new #5m respiratory ward
OL,4,Caimed at cutting A&E waiting times
OL,6,FDirector of Nursing, Kate Holmes,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We've come through (the
OL,8,Fpandemic) and learned from every
OL,9,Faspect in terms of patient care,
OL,10,Fpatient experience, and how we can be
OL,11,Fready for a possible another pandemic,
OL,12,Fwhich we all hope will never happen.
OL,14,F"But we need to be ready and prepared
OL,15,Fshould it do so, to make sure we can
OL,16,Fstill deliver excellent care for
OL,17,Fpatients."
