OL,3,CInside the new #5m respiratory ward
OL,4,Caimed at cutting A&E waiting times
OL,6,FThe new respiratory support unit (RSU)
OL,7,Fis part of a wider project to treat
OL,8,Fall patients with serous breathing or
OL,9,Fheart conditions into the same part of
OL,10,Fthe large Gillingham hospital.
OL,12,FThe vision from Medway Trust leaders
OL,13,Fis for a 'cardio-respiratory village'
OL,14,Fto develop at the site.
OL,16,FThe existing respiratory and
OL,17,Fcardiology wards are at opposite ends
OL,18,Fof the site, inhibiting close working
OL,19,Fbetween the clinic teams.
